settings.description: Fed up with Mario beating them up time and time again, all of the enemies turn giganto! Use the starman to blast your way through these larger-than-life foes.
Esquiva la balas y no te resvales en el hielo, buena suerte.
My First Level! So This is a fun level to play. There's also a secret ending by going to the chest. To do this, you have to step on the note blocks, Step on P-switch, and run to the chest.

Just keep running, and don't stop! Let the triangular blocks guide you!
Difficulty: 2/5
REISSUE: Mario's least threatening foes have come together to create insanity in the sewers. Prod. Code: 105, Rel: 5/25/22 -- 8:56 am. I had no new levels finished, so I'm just pushing this out.
Use the P-wing to dodge the spikes! One mess up and you are dead!

I'm sure every level set needs an underwater stage! And where there is water, there is bound to be a frog somewhere in it!
Difficulty: 4/5

Help the penguin get to its' home by using invisible blocks and other gizmos. Friend request. :) 

Also included is a test room for the directional lift -- it's inclusion was canned b/c it didn't warp
